          - "flowchart LR\n  subgraph App[\"App\"]\n    Xlsx[\"Excel (default data)\"]\n    List[\"Category / toast list\"]\n    Random[\"Random suggestion\"]\n    Fav[\"Favorites\"]\n    DB[\"Core Data(Sqlite)\"]\n  end\n\n  Xlsx -->|\"Bundled default\"| DB\n  DB --> List\n  DB --> Random\n  Fav <--> DB"
      - id: related-stocks-ios
        name: "관련주식검색기 iOS"
        meta: "2017.01 · Mobile · Swift"
        tags[2]: platform:ios,lang:swift
        desc:
          en: "iOS app for finding stocks related to a selected theme or keyword. It shows recommended search terms, favorite stocks, synced stock prices, and push notifications for fast-rising stocks and recommended themes."
          ko: "선택하거나 입력한 테마·키워드와 관련된 주식 종목을 나열하는 iOS 앱. 추천 검색어, 나의 관심주, 종목별 주가 동기화, 실시간 급등주와 추천 테마 푸시 알림을 제공."
        role:
          en: "Sole iOS developer. Built the Swift app with RxSwift/RxCocoa, Core Data favorites, Kakao sharing, and integration with the Node.js/MySQL/GNUBoard backend originally built for the related-stock data."
          ko: "iOS 단독 개발. RxSwift/RxCocoa 기반 Swift 앱, Core Data 관심주 저장, Kakao 공유, 관련주 데이터 제공을 위해 만들었던 Node.js/MySQL/GNUBoard 백엔드 연동을 구현."
        achievement:
          en: "Proposed push notifications for fast-rising and recommended stocks to increase repeat app usage, then added the supporting server/app flow; the Android version's revenue reportedly doubled after the push feature, reaching about ₩3 million per month."
          ko: "앱 재방문을 늘리기 위해 급등주·추천주 푸시 기능을 제안하고 서버/앱 흐름을 추가. 해당 푸시 기능 적용 후 안드로이드 기준 수익이 약 2배 증가해 월 300만 원 수준까지 올랐다고 전달받음."
        tech[6]: Swift,RxSwift,CoreData,KakaoSDK,FCM,"Node.js"
        image: "/images/indie/related-stocks/related-stocks1.png"
        images[6]:
          - "/images/indie/related-stocks/related-stocks1.png"
