          - "flowchart LR\n  Developer[\"App developer\"]\n  App\n\n  subgraph Windows\n    subgraph Board[\"GNUBoard\"]\n      Web\n    end\n\n    subgraph DB\n      subgraph PostTable[\"Post title = keyword\"]\n        CommentTable[\"Comments = stocks related to keyword\"]\n      end\n    end\n\n    subgraph Server[\"App Server\"]\n      REST[\"REST API\"]\n    end\n  end\n\n  Firebase\n  APNS\n  UserApp[\"Other User's App\"]\n\n  Developer -->|Post stock item as comment| Web\n  Board -->|Post| DB\n  Query --> REST\n  REST -->|Query| DB\n  App -->|Request by keyword| Server\n  Server -->|Related /\n  recommended stocks| App\n\n  App -->|Register| Firebase\n  Developer -->|Send Notification| Firebase\n  Firebase --> APNS\n  APNS -->|Notification| UserApp"
      - id: wherewego
        name: "우리어디가"
        meta: "2017.05 · Mobile · Swift"
        tags[3]: platform:ios,lang:swift,framework:swiftui
        desc:
          en: "Location-based tourism guide built on Korea's public TourAPI 3.0. From a chosen location and radius it surfaces nearby attractions, restaurants, cafes and lodging by category, with details, map directions, and tourism info translated into 10 languages; KakaoTalk sharing built in."
          ko: "한국관광공사 공공데이터(TourAPI 3.0) 기반 위치 관광 가이드. 설정한 위치와 반경 내의 관광지·맛집·카페·숙소를 카테고리별로 보여주고, 지도에서 상세 정보와 길찾기를 제공하며 10개 국어로 번역된 관광 정보를 제공. 카카오톡 공유 지원."
        role:
          en: "Sole developer — design to App Store. Built the SwiftUI app (MVVM) on CoreLocation/MapKit and the public TourAPI 3.0, integrated KakaoTalk sharing and Google AdMob, and went through the public-data application/integration process firsthand."
          ko: "단독 개발 — 디자인부터 앱스토어 출시까지. CoreLocation/MapKit과 공공 TourAPI 3.0 위에 SwiftUI(MVVM) 앱을 구현하고, 카카오톡 공유와 Google AdMob을 연동했으며, 공공데이터 신청·연동 절차를 직접 수행."
        achievement:
          en: "Gained hands-on experience applying for and integrating Korean government open data (TourAPI 3.0), shipping a solo SwiftUI app that turns it into a category-based, multi-language nearby-tourism guide with map directions and KakaoTalk sharing."
          ko: "공공데이터(TourAPI 3.0) 신청·연동을 직접 경험하고, 이를 카테고리별·다국어 주변 관광 가이드(지도 길찾기·카카오톡 공유 포함)로 만든 SwiftUI 앱을 단독 출시."
        tech[6]: Swift,SwiftUI,MapKit,CoreLocation,"Tour API",AdMob
