        diagrams[1]:
          - "flowchart LR\n  GDrive[\"Google Drive (Excel, per-version)\"]\n\n  subgraph App[\"공인중개사요약집 (Swift)\"]\n    Download[\"Version-checked download\"]\n    Parse[\"Sheet → Table\"]\n    Study[\"Study: zoom / search / favorites / resume\"]\n    Quiz[\"Auto-generated quiz\"]\n    Notify[\"Local notification\"]\n    DB[\"Core Data\"]\n  end\n\n  GDrive -->|\"If new version\"| Download\n  Download --> Parse\n  Parse --> Study\n  Study --> Quiz\n  Study <--> DB\n  Notify -.->|\"Study time\"| Study"
  - id: siwonschool
    name: "SIWONSCHOOL(SJWInternational)"
    when: "2018.06 — 2021.05"
    role:
      en: "iOS Developer"
      ko: "EduTech 개발팀 / iOS 개발자"
    cur: false
    projects[9]:
      - id: lectureroom
        name: "시원스쿨"
        meta: "2018.06 – 2021.05 · Mobile · Swift"
        tags[2]: platform:ios,lang:swift
        desc:
          en: "Representative Siwonschool iOS app for taking language courses across the service. It supports video/audio playback, minimized and full-screen playback, Picture in Picture, landscape/iPad layouts, background downloads, offline playback, section repeat, and gesture controls for volume and brightness."
          ko: "시원스쿨의 모든 언어 강의를 수강할 수 있는 대표 iOS 앱. 영상/음원 재생, 최소화·전체화면·PIP·Landscape, 백그라운드 다운로드와 오프라인 재생, iPad/Landscape 대응, 구간 반복, 제스처 기반 볼륨·밝기 조정을 지원."
        role:
          en: "iOS developer from zero-base development through three years of maintenance. Led planning review and server-progress coordination during early project stagnation, designed reusable minimized playback across screens, built iPad playback layouts, PiP/background playback controls, background download task queues, XCUITest automation, VoiceOver improvements, and RxSwift + MVVM structure."
          ko: "Zero-Base iOS 개발부터 3년간 유지보수까지 담당. 초기 프로젝트 정체 상황에서 기획 검토와 서버 진행 관리를 주도하고, 화면 전반에 재사용 가능한 최소화/복원 구조, iPad 전용 재생 화면, PIP/백그라운드 재생 제어, 백그라운드 다운로드 Task Queue, XCUITest 자동화, VoiceOver 개선, RxSwift + MVVM 구조를 구현."
        achievement:
          en: "Built and maintained the representative lecture app from scratch, recovered momentum in a stalled early project by leading planning/server coordination, and proposed/implemented review prompts that helped the app reach and keep a 4.7 rating after offboarding."
          ko: "대표 강의 앱을 처음부터 개발하고 3년간 유지보수. 초기 정체 상황에서 기획/서버 진행을 주도해 프로젝트 흐름을 회복했으며, 사용자 리뷰 요청 기능을 제안·구현해 평점 4.7 달성과 퇴사 후 유지에 기여."
        tech[7]: Swift,RxSwift,MVVM,CocoaPods,DRM,AVFoundation,XCUITest
