      - id: real-training
        name: "리얼트레이닝"
        meta: "2018.06 – 2021.05 · Mobile · Swift"
        tags[2]: platform:ios,lang:swift
        desc:
          en: "iOS app for situation-based English speaking practice. Learners watch native-speaker prompts, record their own speech, receive analysis/evaluation, and replay results; maintenance covered SNS login, recording/playback, Firebase integration, Safe Area adaptation, and production stabilization."
          ko: "상황별 원어민 영어를 따라 말하고 녹음·분석·평가받는 iOS 학습 앱. SNS 로그인, 녹음·분석·재생, Firebase 연동, SafeArea 대응과 운영 안정화를 맡음."
        role:
          en: "iOS developer. Took over the app immediately after joining, fixed bugs and server-error cases without a dedicated planner, improved usability based on comments/feedback, handled Safe Area support, and made list UI changes near offboarding."
          ko: "iOS 개발 담당. 입사 직후 프로젝트를 인수해 별도 기획자나 명확한 요구사항이 부족한 상태에서 버그 수정, 서버 오류 대응, 댓글/피드백 기반 편의성 개선, SafeArea 대응, 퇴사 직전 리스트 UI 수정까지 처리."
        achievement:
          en: "Stabilized a live learning app after takeover: reduced production friction through bug fixes, server-error handling, Safe Area adaptation, and user-feedback-driven UX improvements while keeping recording, analysis, playback, and SNS login flows operational."
          ko: "인수 직후 운영 중인 학습 앱을 안정화: 버그 수정, 서버 오류 대응, SafeArea 대응, 사용자 피드백 기반 편의성 개선을 진행하며 녹음·분석·재생·SNS 로그인 흐름을 유지."
        tech[5]: Swift,Firebase,Recording,Video,SafeArea
        image: "/images/siwonschool/real-training/real-training1.png"
        images[6]:
          - "/images/siwonschool/real-training/real-training1.png"
          - "/images/siwonschool/real-training/real-training2.png"
          - "/images/siwonschool/real-training/real-training3.png"
          - "/images/siwonschool/real-training/real-training4.png"
          - "/images/siwonschool/real-training/real-training5.png"
          - "/images/siwonschool/real-training/real-training6.png"
        diagrams[1]:
          - "flowchart LR\n  User[\"Learner\"]\n  Server\n\n  subgraph App\n    Login[\"login\"]\n    Video[\"Play Native speaker video\"]\n    Record[\"Speech recording\"]\n    Library\n  end\n\n  Firebase\n  Facebook\n  KakaoTalk\n\n  Server --> Video\n\n  Video -->|Replay| Video\n\n  User --> Login\n  Login --> Server\n  Login --> Firebase\n  Login --> Facebook\n  Login --> KakaoTalk\n\n  User --> Record\n  Record -->|Analyze| Library\n  Library -->|Result| User"
      - id: victoeic-voca
        name: "빅토익 보카"
        meta: "2019.01 – 2021.05 · Mobile · Swift"
        tags[2]: platform:ios,lang:swift
        desc:
          en: "iOS version of the Big TOEIC Voca vocabulary app — previously Android-only. Learners browse TOEIC word books, unlock content via in-app purchase, study with card-style UI, bookmark words, group vocabulary, and play MP3 audio with background playback and Remote Control support."
          ko: "Android로만 존재하던 빅토익 보카 iOS 버전. 책 선택·인앱 결제·단어카드·북마크·단어장 그룹·MP3 다운로드·백그라운드 재생·Remote Control을 지원."
        role:
          en: "Sole iOS developer. Received a project where the spec, design, and existing Android app were all inconsistent, independently determined the development direction, proposed and implemented an in-app purchase model, and built all features from scratch including background audio playback and Card UI."
          ko: "iOS 단독 개발. 기획서·디자인·기존 앱이 모두 불일치하는 상태에서 개발 방향을 직접 정립. 인앱 결제 모델 제안·구축, 백그라운드 음원 재생·Card UI 포함 전 기능 개발."
        achievement:
          en: "Delivered the first iOS version of an Android-only TOEIC vocabulary app, independently resolving spec/design inconsistencies to drive it to release, and transformed it from a book appendix into a standalone revenue service via in-app purchase."
          ko: "Android 전용 TOEIC 단어장 부록 앱을 iOS로 독자 개발. 기획·디자인·앱 불일치 상황을 직접 해결해 출시로 이끌고, 인앱 결제 모델 도입으로 독립적인 수익 서비스로 전환."
        tech[5]: Swift,AVFoundation,StoreKit,CocoaPods,CDN
        image: "/images/siwonschool/victoeic-voca/victoeic-voca1.jpeg"
        images[3]:
          - "/images/siwonschool/victoeic-voca/victoeic-voca1.jpeg"
          - "/images/siwonschool/victoeic-voca/victoeic-voca2.jpeg"
          - "/images/siwonschool/victoeic-voca/victoeic-voca3.jpeg"
        diagrams[1]:
          - "flowchart LR\n  User[\"Learner\"]\n  AppStore[\"App Store\"]\n  CDN\n  Server\n  CocoaPods[\"Shared CocoaPods\\n(with 시원스쿨)\"]\n\n  subgraph iOS\n    subgraph App\n      Books[\"Book List\"]\n\n      subgraph Study[\"Study\"]\n        subgraph Card[\"Word Cards\"]\n          Audio\n        end\n        Bookmark[\"Bookmark\"]\n\n        Lecture\n      end\n\n      Player[\"Video Player\"]\n      Group[\"Vocab Group\"]\n    end\n\n    Background\n    BGPlay[\"Background Play\"]\n    Remote[\"Remote Control\"]\n  end\n\n  User --> Books\n  Server -->|REST API| Books\n  Books -->|In App Purchase| AppStore\n  AppStore -->|Unlock| Books\n  Books --> Study\n\n  CDN -->|Download MP3| Audio\n\n  Lecture --> Player\n\n  CocoaPods -->|Install| Player\n\n  Player --> Background\n  Background --> BGPlay\n  Background --> Remote\n\n  Audio --> Background\n\n  Bookmark --> Cards\n  Card -->|Add| Bookmark"
      - id: korean-lecture
        name: "React Native 선행 학습"
        meta: "2019.04 – 2019.06 · Mobile · React Native"
        tags[2]: platform:ios,lang:reactnative
        desc:
          en: "Proof-of-concept and internal R&D project to evaluate React Native for an upcoming Korean-language lecture app. Rebuilt Siwonschool's [Home] and [Free Lecture] screens in React Native, explored server communication and DRM player integration, and produced internal training documentation for the team."
          ko: "한국어 강의 앱 신규 개발을 앞두고 React Native 기술 검증을 위한 사내 PoC 프로젝트. 시원스쿨 [홈]·[무료강의] 화면을 React Native로 재구현하고, 서버 통신·DRM 플레이어 연동을 탐색. 팀 내 교육 자료 작성·배포."
        role:
          en: "Self-directed R&D. Independently continued learning and prototyping after team momentum stalled, rebuilt existing screens to validate feasibility, and authored internal training docs."
          ko: "자기주도 R&D. 팀 진행이 중단된 이후에도 독자적으로 학습·프로토타이핑을 지속. 기존 화면 재구현으로 가능성을 검증하고 내부 교육 자료 작성."
        achievement:
          en: "Independently drove a React Native PoC for a planned Korean lecture app after team-led momentum stalled — rebuilt two production screens, explored DRM integration, and delivered internal training docs that raised team readiness even though the project was ultimately cancelled."
          ko: "팀 주도가 중단된 상황에서도 React Native PoC를 독자 완성. 실 서비스 화면 2개 재구현·DRM 연동 탐색·교육 자료 배포로 팀 역량에 기여. 프로젝트는 최종 취소."
        tech[3]: "React Native",JavaScript,DRM
        image: null
        diagrams[1]:
          - "flowchart LR\n  Server\n  NPM\n\n  subgraph App[\"React Native PoC\\nof 시원스쿨\"]\n    Home[\"Home Screen\"]\n    Free[\"Free Lecture Screen\"]\n    DRM[\"DRM Library\"]\n    Player[\"Video Player\"]\n  end\n\n  Team\n  Docs[\"Training Documentation\"]\n\n  Server -->|REST API| Home\n  Server -->|REST API| Free\n  Home --> DRM\n  Free --> DRM\n  DRM -->|Decode| Player\n  App -->|Export Experience| Docs\n  NPM -->|Install| Player\n  Docs --> Team"
      - id: word-rocket
        name: "단어 로켓 게임"
        meta: "2019.07 – 2019.09 · Mobile · Unity"
        tags[2]: platform:ios,lang:swift
        desc:
          en: "Unity-based word rocket game and iOS integration PoC for Siwonschool. A spaceship auto-moves through space collecting alphabet letters in order to form words fetched from the server. Researched and successfully embedded Unity as a library inside the existing Siwonschool iOS app."
          ko: "시원스쿨을 위한 Unity 기반 단어 로켓 게임 및 iOS 연동 PoC. 우주선이 자동 이동하며 서버에서 가져온 단어의 알파벳을 순서대로 수집. Unity를 기존 iOS 앱에 라이브러리로 내장하는 데 성공."
        role:
          en: "Self-directed R&D. Built the full Unity game, researched Unity-as-Library integration with iOS, successfully embedded it in the Siwonschool app, and produced internal training docs."
          ko: "자기주도 R&D. Unity 게임 개발, iOS 라이브러리 내장 연구·성공, 교육 자료 작성."
        achievement:
          en: "Validated Unity-as-Library integration with an existing iOS app by building a word-collection rocket game in Unity and successfully embedding it in the Siwonschool app — then documented the process as internal training material."
          ko: "Unity를 기존 iOS 앱에 라이브러리로 내장하는 가능성을 검증. 단어 로켓 게임을 직접 개발해 시원스쿨 앱 내장에 성공하고 교육 자료로 정리·배포."
        tech[3]: Unity,Swift,"Unity as Library"
        image: null
        diagrams[1]:
          - "flowchart LR\n  Server\n\n  subgraph Unity[\"Unity Game\"]\n    Word[\"Word Data\"]\n    Letters[\"Letters\"]\n    Rocket[\"Rocket (Auto Move)\"]\n    Touch[\"Touch Direction\"]\n    Collect[\"Letter Collection\"]\n  end\n\n  subgraph App\n    UnityLib[\"Unity as Library\"]\n  end\n\n  Docs[\"Training Documentation\"]\n  Team\n\n  Server -->|Random Word| Letters\n  Letters --> Collect\n  Rocket --> Touch\n  Rocket --> Collect\n  Unity -->|Embed| UnityLib\n  UnityLib -->|기반| Docs\n  Docs --> Team"
      - id: lectureroom-b2b
        name: "시원스쿨 B2B"
        meta: "2019.08 – 2019.09 · Mobile · Swift"
        tags[2]: platform:ios,lang:swift
        desc:
          en: "B2B variant of the Siwonschool lecture app for corporate users. Shares the full codebase via a common Xcode Workspace, with B2B-specific login and customer service contacts branched using Swift preprocessor macros and a separate Storyboard — minimizing duplication while keeping both apps maintainable."
          ko: "시원스쿨 강의 앱의 기업 전용 B2B 버전. 동일 Xcode Workspace 내 공통 소스를 공유하고, Swift preprocessor와 별도 Storyboard로 기업 전용 로그인·연락처만 분기 처리."
        role:
          en: "Sole iOS developer. Designed the multi-target workspace structure, configured the multi-project Podfile, and implemented preprocessor-based branching for all B2B-specific screens."
          ko: "iOS 단독 개발. 멀티 타겟 Workspace 구조 설계, 다중 프로젝트 Podfile 구성, preprocessor 분기 처리 구현."
        achievement:
          en: "Delivered a B2B white-label of the Siwonschool app by structuring shared code across a common Xcode Workspace, using Swift preprocessor branching and separate Storyboards to swap only B2B-specific login, server, and contact screens — zero duplication."
          ko: "시원스쿨 앱을 공통 Xcode Workspace 구조로 공유하고 Swift preprocessor + 별도 Storyboard로 기업 전용 로그인·서버·연락처만 교체하는 B2B 버전 출시. 중복 개발 없음."
        tech[4]: Swift,Xcode,"Preprocessor",CocoaPods
        image: "/images/siwonschool/lectureroom-b2b/lectureroom-b2b1.jpeg"
        images[2]:
          - "/images/siwonschool/lectureroom-b2b/lectureroom-b2b1.jpeg"
          - "/images/siwonschool/lectureroom-b2b/lectureroom-b2b2.jpeg"
        diagrams[1]:
          - "flowchart LR\n  subgraph Workspace[\"Xcode Workspace\"]\n    Preprocessor{\"#if B2B?\"}\n\n    subgraph B2CTarget[\"B2C Target\"]\n      subgraph B2CLogin[\"B2C Login\"]\n        B2CID[\"User ID\"]\n        B2CContact[\"Customer Center\"]\n      end\n    end\n\n    subgraph B2BTarget[\"B2B Target\"]\n      subgraph B2BLogin[\"B2B Login\"]\n        B2BID[\"User ID\"]\n        B2BCorpID[\"Corp ID\"]\n        B2BContact[\"Corp Customer Center\"]\n        B2BStory[\"B2B Storyboard\"]\n      end\n    end\n  end\n\n  B2BServer[\"B2B 서버\"]\n  subgraph CocoaPods[\"Podfile\"]\n    CB2B[\"B2B\"]\n    CNormal[\"B2C\"]\n  end\n\n  Preprocessor -->|Y| B2BTarget\n  Preprocessor -->|N| B2CTarget\n  CocoaPods --> Workspace\n  B2BServer --> B2BLogin"
      - id: siwon-alimi
        name: "시원알리미"
        meta: "2019.05 – 2019.06 · Mobile · Swift"
        tags[2]: platform:ios,lang:swift
        desc:
          en: "Internal iOS app for Siwonschool intranet notifications. Solved the problem of missing important alerts due to frequent intranet logouts — detects login state via WebView JavaScript injection and delivers personalized push notifications through Firebase topic subscriptions without additional server development."
          ko: "시원스쿨 인트라넷 알림을 위한 사내 iOS 앱. 잦은 로그아웃으로 알림을 놓치는 문제를 해결. WebView JavaScript injection으로 로그인 감지·수신함 자동 이동, Firebase topic 구독으로 별도 토큰 저장 없이 개인화 푸시 전달."
        role:
          en: "Sole developer. Identified the pain point, proposed the solution architecture (JS injection + Firebase topic), and built the full app."
          ko: "단독 개발. 문제를 직접 발굴하고 해결 방식(JS injection + Firebase topic)을 제안·설계·구현."
        achievement:
          en: "Solved intranet notification failures from frequent logouts by building an iOS app that uses WebView JavaScript injection for login detection and Firebase topic-based push — zero extra server development required."
          ko: "인트라넷 잦은 로그아웃으로 인한 알림 누락 문제를 iOS 앱으로 해결. WebView JS injection으로 로그인 감지·자동 이동, Firebase topic 구독으로 추가 서버 개발 없이 개인화 푸시 구현."
        tech[4]: Swift,WebView,"JavaScript Injection",Firebase
        image: null
        diagrams[1]:
          - "flowchart LR\n  User[\"Employee\"]\n  Server[\"Intranet Server\"]\n\n  subgraph App\n    subgraph WebView\n      Intranet[\"Intranet\"]\n    end\n    JSInject[\"JavaScript Injection\"]\n    Inbox[\"Move to InBox\"]\n  end\n\n  Firebase[\"Firebase\"]\n\n  User -->|Run| App\n  WebView -->|Inject| JSInject\n  JSInject -->|\"Detect Login\"| Inbox\n  JSInject -->|\"Register ID as topic\"| Firebase\n  Firebase -->|\"Personal Notification\"| User\n  Server -->|\"Send Notification to topics\"| Firebase\n  Inbox --> Intranet"
      - id: siwon-pen
        name: "시원스쿨펜"
        meta: "2019.11 – 2021.05 · Mobile · React Native"
        tags[2]: platform:ios,lang:reactnative
        desc:
          en: "Companion app for 시원스쿨's smart-pen hardware — the pen scans hidden patterns in textbooks to trigger audio playback, and this app provides word cards, lecture player, quiz, and my-vocabulary. I contributed the initial React Native lecture-player code, then owned post-launch maintenance: replaced ScrollView with FlatList for word cards, introduced Appium regression testing, and wired Firebase Analytics."
          ko: "시원스쿨 자동암기펜 전용 앱. 펜이 교재의 숨겨진 패턴을 인식해 음원을 재생하는 제품에 연동되며, 단어 카드·강의 재생·퀴즈·내단어장 기능 제공. RN 강의 재생 코드를 기여해 앱 출시 기반을 만들고, ScrollView→FlatList 교체로 성능 개선, Appium 자동화 테스트 도입, Firebase Analytics 연동 등 유지보수 담당."
        role:
          en: "React Native code contributor → post-launch maintenance developer."
          ko: "React Native 코드 기여 → 출시 후 유지보수 담당."
        achievement:
          en: "Delivered the initial React Native lecture-player code — built during the prior 선행 학습 project — to the 시원스쿨펜 team, which shipped as the app's core feature. Post-launch, replaced ScrollView with FlatList in word cards to eliminate scroll jank, removed the confirm-tap from quiz flow for instant submission, redesigned my-vocabulary with inline edit/delete, introduced Appium regression coverage, and wired Firebase Analytics to track study-flow patterns."
          ko: "선행 학습 프로젝트에서 구현한 RN 강의 재생 코드를 시원스쿨펜 팀에 제공해 앱의 핵심 기능으로 출시. 출시 후 ScrollView→FlatList 교체로 단어 카드 스크롤 성능 개선, 퀴즈 즉시 제출로 학습 흐름 개선, 내단어장 인라인 편집/삭제 재설계, Appium 회귀 테스트 도입, Firebase Analytics 연동."
        tech[3]: "React Native",Firebase,Appium
